title: Unlimited Signature Spells
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

All of your spells are signature spells. 

That means that if you know a spell, you can heighten it freely by casting it from a higher-level spell slot, up to the maximum level of spell you can cast. 

You can similarly cast any of its lower-level versions without learning them separately.